Package org.dellroad.stuff.vaadin8

Annotation Type FieldBuilder.AbstractMultiSelect

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(METHOD)
@Documented
public static @interface FieldBuilder.AbstractMultiSelect
    Specifies how a Java property should be edited using an AbstractMultiSelect.
    See Also:
    FieldBuilder.AbstractListing, FieldBuilder
